<lb n="9"/>coḻa maṇṭalattu taṉiyūṟ cimaturāntaka
<lb n="10" break="no"/>c catu<hi rend="grantha">rvvedi</hi> maṅkalattu vaṭapiṭākai vittū
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ruṭaiyār tiruvālakkoyil Uṭai
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yanāyaṉār koyiṟ tāṉattārom Ik
